# Vue SOP

- Composition API (`<script setup>`) for new components unless Options-only legacy.
- Props/emits typed (`defineProps` / `defineEmits`); never mutate props.
- Extract composables for shared logic; keep SFCs focused on template + wiring.
- Reactivity: prefer `ref`/`computed` clarity; avoid deep watch when computed suffices.
- Pinia or project store for cross-route state; no ad-hoc global event buses in new code.
- Align with design tokens / CSS conventions; scoped styles or project utility system.
- Tests: Vitest + Vue Test Utils when present; test user-visible behavior.
- Async: handle loading/error in UI; cancel in-flight requests on unmount when using fetch.
- Before done: `type-check`, `lint`, `build` (or project verify script).
